        "TileImage": "$($repository f7164cc2-71b8-45d2-9c8e-a0bfefdb1403).Image",
        "Description": "Agent 47 is bored of hitman-ing. It gets too tedious, he ends up getting shot all of the time, and he&apos;s annoyed of that woman&apos;s bloody awful voice. He has a new job as the art crew, however his co-workers bully him for being bald and having a barcode at the back of his head like some ASDA orange.\rIt is time for him to take his revenge - he cannot be seen doing anything suspicious as he wants to keep his job. \r\rTime to get up to some hitman chaos just like the olden days.",
